Service Providers - Main service, the central place of all Laravel application bootstrapping.
					config/app.php, the list of the service provider classes

Service Container - Managing class dependencies and performing dependency injection.

Operation 
Route - routes/web.php
	http://your-app.test/user
	Route::get('/user', 'UserController@index');

Middleware
	If you want a middleware to run during every HTTP request to your application, list the middleware class in the $middleware property of your app/Http/Kernel.php class.